'''哈珀科林斯出版集團'''（{{lang-en|'''HarperCollins Publishers LLC'''}}）是世界最大的出版公司之一，屬於[[新聞集團|新聞集團]]旗下，總部位於[[紐約|紐約]]。其名稱來自1987年併入的美國出版公司Harper & Row和1990年併入的英國出版公司William Collins。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.observer.com/2008/its-official-jane-friedman-out-harpercollins-her-deputy-effective-immediately|title=It's Official: Jane Friedman Out at HarperCollins, Her Deputy Up 'Effective Immediately'|last=Neyfakh|first=Leon|date=June 4, 2008|work=[[The_New_York_Observer|The New York Observer]]|accessdate=26 November 2010|archive-date=2009-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091004160011/http://www.observer.com/2008/its-official-jane-friedman-out-harpercollins-her-deputy-effective-immediately|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==
[[File:The_news_building_SE1.jpg|thumb]]附近的英国總部]]

1990年蘇格蘭出版公司William Collins被[[魯伯特·默多克|魯伯特·默多克]]的[[新聞集團|新聞集團]]買下，加上之前收購的Harper & Row，合併成為哈珀柯林斯。公司的標誌也是原來兩家公司合成的。

1999年新聞集團買下[[William_Morrow_&_Company|William Morrow & Company]]和[[Avon_Books|Avon Books]]，現此二者都在哈珀柯林斯的名義下出版。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.newscorp.com/news/news_077.html|title=News Corporation Announces Plans To Acquire William Morrow & Company And Avon Books From The Hearst Corporation|date=June 17, 1999|publisher=News Corporation|accessdate=August 6, 2012|location=New York|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061209220010/http://www.newscorp.com/news/news_077.html|archivedate=2006-12-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 2011年，哈珀柯林斯宣稱將購買蘇格蘭出版公司[[托馬斯尼爾森|托馬斯尼爾森]]，<ref>{{cite journal |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date=October 31, 2011 |title=HarperCollins to Acquire Thomas Nelson |journal=''[[Publishers_Weekly|Publishers Weekly]]'' |volume= |issue= |pages= |publisher= |doi= |url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/industry-news/industry-deals/article/49334-harpercollins-to-acquire-thomas-nelson.html |accessdate= |archive-date=2012-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120717234635/http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/industry-news/industry-deals/article/49334-harpercollins-to-acquire-thomas-nelson.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2012年7月11日交易完成。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.thomasnelsoncorporate.com/2012/07/harpercollins-finalizes-acquisition-of-thomas-nelson/ |title=HarperCollins Finalizes Acquisition of Thomas Nelson |author=Casey Francis |publisher=Thomas Nelson, Inc. |date=July 11, 2012 |accessdate=August 6, 2012 |archive-date=2012-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120914034518/http://www.thomasnelsoncorporate.com/2012/07/harpercollins-finalizes-acquisition-of-thomas-nelson/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===美國訴蘋果案===
2012年4月，[[美國司法部|美國司法部]]宣佈《美國訴蘋果案》（United States v. Apple Inc.）結案，[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]和哈珀柯林斯等幾家公司因故意固定電子書價格以壟斷電子書業務、排擠[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]，而被判違反[[休曼法案|休曼法案]]<ref name="washington post DOJ sues">{{cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/justice-department-files-suit-against-apple-publishers-report-says/2012/04/11/gIQAzyXSAT_story.html | title=Justice Department sues Apple, publishers over e-book prices | work=The Washington Post | date=April 11, 2012 | accessdate=June 1, 2014 | author=Mui, Ylan Q. and Hayley Tsukayama | archive-date=2014-10-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006074356/http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/justice-department-files-suit-against-apple-publishers-report-says/2012/04/11/gIQAzyXSAT_story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。次年12月，聯邦法官要求被告將資金匯入一個基金會，以彌補因價格壟斷而遭受損失的顧客。<ref name="usatoday settlements rolling out">{{cite news | url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2014/03/25/amazon-settlements-ebooks/6869033/ | title=E-book price fixing settlements rolling out | work=USA Today | date=March 25, 2014 | accessdate=June 1, 2014 | author=Molina, Brett | archive-date=2019-12-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224210523/https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2014/03/25/amazon-settlements-ebooks/6869033/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

